---
title: "Noema — User Flow: Search & Context Generation"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Svelte Frontend
    participant Cmd as Command Router
    participant QP as Query Parser
    participant Emb as Embedding Engine
    participant VS as Vector Search
    participant BM as BM25 Search
    participant RRF as RRF Ranker
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant LLM as AI Engine

    Note over User,LLM: Search Flow

    User->>UI: Types "budget reports Q1 revenue"
    UI->>Cmd: search({ text: "...", filters: [] })
    Cmd->>QP: parse(query_text)
    QP-->>Cmd: ParsedQuery { semantic, keyword, filters }

    par Parallel Search
        Cmd->>Emb: embed_query(semantic_text)
        Emb-->>VS: query_vector [384 dims]
        VS->>DB: KNN search (top 100)
        DB-->>VS: vector_results
    and
        Cmd->>BM: fts_search(keyword_text)
        BM->>DB: FTS5 MATCH query
        DB-->>BM: keyword_results
    end

    VS-->>RRF: ranked vector hits
    BM-->>RRF: ranked keyword hits
    RRF->>RRF: merge + score (k=60)
    RRF->>DB: fetch file metadata for top 20
    DB-->>RRF: file entries
    RRF-->>Cmd: SearchResults[20]
    Cmd-->>UI: results + snippets + scores
    UI-->>User: Display ranked results

    Note over User,LLM: Context Generation Flow (on demand)

    User->>UI: Clicks "Generate Context" on a result
    UI->>Cmd: generate_context(file_id)
    Cmd->>DB: get file content/chunks
    DB-->>Cmd: file content
    Cmd->>LLM: generate(content, prompt)

    Note right of LLM: Runs async in dedicated thread.<br/>User can continue browsing.

    LLM-->>Cmd: AIContext { summary, entities, tags }
    Cmd->>DB: store context (versioned)
    Cmd-->>UI: Event::ContextGenerated(file_id)
    UI-->>User: Show AI summary, entities, suggested tags
    User->>UI: Edits summary, accepts some tags
    UI->>Cmd: update_annotation(file_id, edits)
    Cmd->>DB: update (user_edited = true)
